WEBVTT

00:01:15.700 --> 00:01:20.940
=About Love=

00:01:21.000 --> 00:01:23.940
=Episode 25=

00:01:24.710 --> 00:01:26.200
Are you free tomorrow morning?

00:01:26.500 --> 00:01:27.680
I'll come over to your place.

00:01:27.890 --> 00:01:29.710
Cashed out from
closing the store and selling the gear.

00:01:29.710 --> 00:01:30.790
And the money I owe Bei.

00:01:30.790 --> 00:01:31.710
Let's settle the accounts.

00:01:31.950 --> 00:01:32.790
I'll pay it back with you.

00:01:35.870 --> 00:01:36.710
No rush.

00:01:39.590 --> 00:01:40.430
Oh, and one more thing.

00:01:41.000 --> 00:01:42.680
The property handover
can't happen until Monday.

00:01:42.680 --> 00:01:43.680
Need you to go there

00:01:43.680 --> 00:01:44.710
and return the keys to them.

00:01:50.680 --> 00:01:51.950
Why don't you do it yourself?

00:01:54.350 --> 00:01:55.560
An old classmate

00:01:55.850 --> 00:01:57.510
asked me to work as
a travel photographer.

00:01:57.970 --> 00:01:59.070
The headquarters is in Yunnan.

00:02:00.680 --> 00:02:01.520
I said yes.

00:02:01.870 --> 00:02:02.710
I'm leaving tomorrow.

00:02:02.920 --> 00:02:03.760
Yunnan?

00:02:04.680 --> 00:02:05.950
That's so far away.

00:02:05.950 --> 00:02:06.920
How can you go there alone?

00:02:07.820 --> 00:02:08.910
Why wouldn't I be able to?

00:02:09.740 --> 00:02:11.520
It's the perfect chance for
a change of scenery

00:02:11.520 --> 00:02:12.430
and a change of mood.

00:02:12.430 --> 00:02:17.580
(Qian Chang Photography Studio)

00:02:17.590 --> 00:02:18.430
I'll take off then.

00:02:21.120 --> 00:02:22.360
Mingming, that...

00:02:38.940 --> 00:02:41.100
(Qian Chang Photography Studio)

00:02:41.120 --> 00:02:42.080
Qian Chang.

00:02:45.750 --> 00:02:46.840
It's opening in a few days.

00:02:46.840 --> 00:02:47.870
You still haven't told me

00:02:47.870 --> 00:02:49.280
Qian Chang's meaning.

00:02:49.280 --> 00:02:51.000
It's actually

00:02:51.310 --> 00:02:53.870
a love poem from The Book of Songs
that I love so much.

00:02:54.470 --> 00:02:55.310
A love poem?

00:02:56.910 --> 00:02:59.400
(Qian Chang)
If you miss me, across the Qin River.

00:02:59.630 --> 00:03:01.910
If you don't,
there are plenty of others who will.

00:03:02.240 --> 00:03:03.590
That's the Mad Youth's Madness.

00:03:04.870 --> 00:03:05.710
What does that mean?

00:03:07.680 --> 00:03:09.030
Basically, it means

00:03:09.310 --> 00:03:11.150
if you love me and miss me,

00:03:11.150 --> 00:03:12.590
then come be with me.

00:03:12.590 --> 00:03:13.430
Otherwise,

00:03:13.430 --> 00:03:15.030
there will be someone else who will.

00:03:15.310 --> 00:03:16.520
Of course I'll be with you.

00:03:17.430 --> 00:03:19.120
No matter where you go, near or far,

00:03:19.400 --> 00:03:20.240
I'll follow you.

00:03:20.710 --> 00:03:22.430
Really, kiddo?

00:03:22.430 --> 00:03:23.270
Definitely.

00:03:26.780 --> 00:03:33.820
(Qian Chang)

00:03:33.820 --> 00:03:34.900
(Shangyang, Yubin)

00:03:35.700 --> 00:03:36.300
(Window, aisle)

00:03:36.560 --> 00:03:37.840
Excuse me, my seat's inside.

00:03:37.840 --> 00:03:39.150
Could you please let me through?

00:03:44.440 --> 00:03:45.430
I need to move my suitcase.

00:03:45.680 --> 00:03:46.520
Just a second.

00:03:51.310 --> 00:03:52.150
It's fine.

00:03:55.120 --> 00:03:56.710
Sorry, did I step on you?

00:03:59.960 --> 00:04:01.280
I didn't mean to. I'm sorry.

00:04:15.150 --> 00:04:17.670
♪I'll stay insane♪

00:04:17.670 --> 00:04:21.020
♪When you call my name♪

00:04:24.130 --> 00:04:28.860
♪You know what I'll say♪

00:04:45.950 --> 00:04:48.040
♪At night♪

00:04:48.040 --> 00:04:52.770
♪I wonder if it will go away♪

00:04:53.820 --> 00:04:55.710
♪At dawn♪

00:04:55.910 --> 00:05:01.100
♪I wonder if I will be okay♪

00:05:02.040 --> 00:05:08.850
♪I lie awake♪

00:05:09.200 --> 00:05:13.020
♪Thinking about how to stay the same♪

00:05:13.280 --> 00:05:17.320
♪Thinking about how to stay insane♪

00:05:17.890 --> 00:05:24.750
♪I lie awake♪

00:05:25.200 --> 00:05:28.900
♪Thinking there's nothing I could say♪

00:05:29.200 --> 00:05:31.530
♪Only to lie and lie awake♪

00:05:31.560 --> 00:05:32.950
- You alright?
- I'm fine.

00:05:32.950 --> 00:05:33.790
Okay.

00:05:37.000 --> 00:05:37.840
Almost there.

00:05:38.120 --> 00:05:38.960
We've arrived.

00:05:45.630 --> 00:05:47.000
- You okay?
- I'm fine.

00:05:47.190 --> 00:05:48.030
Feeling dizzy.

00:05:48.360 --> 00:05:49.200
Thanks.

00:05:49.600 --> 00:05:50.440
It's nothing.

00:05:50.630 --> 00:05:51.560
Thanks for the hand.

00:05:51.560 --> 00:05:52.400
No problem.

00:05:54.600 --> 00:05:55.750
I'll go now.

00:05:56.600 --> 00:05:57.790
- Alright.
- Goodbye.

00:05:58.360 --> 00:05:59.200
Goodbye.

00:06:07.960 --> 00:06:14.880
♪I lie awake♪

00:06:17.120 --> 00:06:18.680
(We'll definitely meet again)

00:06:19.230 --> 00:06:24.260
♪Only to lie and lie awake♪

00:06:25.670 --> 00:06:29.420
♪Everyday♪

00:06:43.680 --> 00:06:44.800
I'm sorry. We're closed.

00:07:00.280 --> 00:07:01.160
The bottom's secured.

00:07:01.160 --> 00:07:02.480
Want me to wrap the top too?

00:07:03.000 --> 00:07:04.310
No, this is fine.

00:07:04.830 --> 00:07:05.670
Thanks.

00:07:05.800 --> 00:07:06.640
Take care.

00:07:30.420 --> 00:07:31.780
(Archery Club)

00:07:32.430 --> 00:07:34.190
We used to hang out here a lot.

00:07:35.000 --> 00:07:35.910
Let's play one more round.

00:07:36.720 --> 00:07:37.560
I'm not in the mood.

00:07:38.070 --> 00:07:39.240
Just say what's on your mind.

00:07:40.600 --> 00:07:41.560
Lin Chen said

00:07:42.630 --> 00:07:44.190
the reason you got so mad that day

00:07:44.510 --> 00:07:45.480
all goes back to

00:07:45.720 --> 00:07:46.680
what happened before.

00:07:46.680 --> 00:07:47.870
I don't want to talk about him.

00:07:48.630 --> 00:07:49.680
Why not?

00:07:54.190 --> 00:07:55.390
What if I told you

00:07:56.510 --> 00:07:58.390
I was never with him,

00:07:59.870 --> 00:08:00.750
would you believe me?

00:08:05.950 --> 00:08:06.790
That day,

00:08:07.040 --> 00:08:08.360
I dragged my suitcase

00:08:09.600 --> 00:08:11.430
and waited for you in the hallway.

00:08:14.190 --> 00:08:15.190
If you'd just come out,

00:08:16.270 --> 00:08:17.390
you would have seen me.

00:08:19.000 --> 00:08:20.000
But you didn't.

00:08:23.360 --> 00:08:24.870
After all these years together,

00:08:25.160 --> 00:08:26.310
how could you be so cold?

00:08:26.750 --> 00:08:27.680
I just couldn't let it go.

00:08:28.310 --> 00:08:29.950
So I got close to Lin Chen on purpose,

00:08:30.800 --> 00:08:32.390
and told everyone around us.

00:08:33.120 --> 00:08:34.120
Let them tell you

00:08:34.600 --> 00:08:35.550
I'm with him now.

00:08:37.120 --> 00:08:38.510
I just wanted you to know

00:08:39.270 --> 00:08:40.550
it wasn't you who left me.

00:08:41.630 --> 00:08:42.750
I'm the one who left you.

00:08:46.150 --> 00:08:47.240
You wanted to punish me.

00:08:49.150 --> 00:08:50.030
Well, you succeeded.

00:08:51.550 --> 00:08:53.960
I told myself a thousand times
to let go.

00:08:55.150 --> 00:08:56.360
But I just can't.

00:08:56.930 --> 00:08:58.480
I don't believe
you don't love me anymore.

00:09:00.100 --> 00:09:01.510
Otherwise, what was Zhen Guan to you?

00:09:03.080 --> 00:09:04.670
Once I finally calmed down,

00:09:05.510 --> 00:09:06.720
I swallowed my pride,

00:09:07.550 --> 00:09:08.670
set my principles aside,

00:09:09.790 --> 00:09:11.000
and planned to come find you.

00:09:12.480 --> 00:09:13.360
Then I found out

00:09:14.750 --> 00:09:16.200
you were already with someone else.

00:09:18.080 --> 00:09:18.920
Xiaoxi.

00:09:19.650 --> 00:09:20.600
You scared me to death.

00:09:21.080 --> 00:09:21.920
What's wrong?

00:09:22.630 --> 00:09:23.470
I thought...

00:09:24.270 --> 00:09:25.670
I thought someone was following me.

00:09:26.750 --> 00:09:27.590
Following you?

00:09:29.080 --> 00:09:29.920
It's nothing.

00:09:30.150 --> 00:09:31.840
Maybe I just haven't slept well lately.

00:09:33.120 --> 00:09:34.120
Come on, let's go home.

00:09:37.480 --> 00:09:38.320
I was thinking...

00:09:39.000 --> 00:09:40.150
If I tell you...

00:09:41.240 --> 00:09:42.840
I'm getting married to Lin Chen,

00:09:43.670 --> 00:09:44.960
would you try to stop me?

00:09:47.600 --> 00:09:48.910
Do you still love me or not?

00:09:58.870 --> 00:09:59.710
Sorry.

00:10:03.550 --> 00:10:04.840
Come sit in my store for a bit.

00:10:04.840 --> 00:10:05.680
Sure.

00:10:06.120 --> 00:10:08.270
I've been okay lately. How about you?

00:10:08.630 --> 00:10:09.470
I'm fine.

00:10:19.630 --> 00:10:20.470
I'm sorry.

00:10:48.320 --> 00:10:50.550
So you brought me here just to see this?

00:10:51.270 --> 00:10:52.150
Do you know her?

00:10:54.270 --> 00:10:55.630
She is Zhen, right?

00:10:57.320 --> 00:10:59.000
Bei told me about them.

00:11:00.080 --> 00:11:01.360
Including today's plans?

00:11:01.910 --> 00:11:02.910
What do you mean?

00:11:04.000 --> 00:11:05.390
We're all adults.

00:11:05.390 --> 00:11:06.790
Who doesn't have a past?

00:11:08.240 --> 00:11:09.840
Am I supposed to be upset

00:11:09.840 --> 00:11:10.840
just because

00:11:11.120 --> 00:11:12.440
my boyfriend met his ex here?

00:11:14.000 --> 00:11:15.150
That's way too childish.

00:11:15.840 --> 00:11:16.680
I know.

00:11:17.240 --> 00:11:18.720
Holding back a little

00:11:18.870 --> 00:11:20.720
is smarter than saying nothing at all.

00:11:22.120 --> 00:11:23.910
But the story Bei told you

00:11:24.320 --> 00:11:25.910
is definitely missing a key part.

00:11:28.480 --> 00:11:30.030
The night you met,

00:11:32.120 --> 00:11:33.200
Zhen came to the store.

00:11:38.030 --> 00:11:39.390
Hello, ma'am, welcome.

00:11:39.390 --> 00:11:41.320
(Zhen Guan)

00:11:41.320 --> 00:11:42.160
Ma'am?

00:11:42.630 --> 00:11:44.030
Hello. How can I help you?

00:11:44.390 --> 00:11:45.360
I'm here to see your boss.

00:11:45.520 --> 00:11:46.870
Do you have an appointment with him?

00:11:46.870 --> 00:11:48.030
No appointment needed. Where is he?

00:11:49.440 --> 00:11:50.870
- He...
- Ma'am, sorry.

00:11:50.900 --> 00:11:52.000
Customers aren't allowed upstairs.

00:11:52.510 --> 00:11:53.720
I know your boss.

00:11:53.720 --> 00:11:55.240
Could you call him if it's convenient?

00:11:55.440 --> 00:11:56.280
Bei!

00:11:57.750 --> 00:11:58.590
Bei!

00:11:58.840 --> 00:12:01.120
Bei, come out for a sec.

00:12:01.120 --> 00:12:01.960
- No going up.
- Mingming.

00:12:03.720 --> 00:12:04.560
Let her come up.

00:12:22.240 --> 00:12:23.200
What brings you to me?

00:12:29.670 --> 00:12:30.510
What do you mean?

00:12:36.960 --> 00:12:37.800
I...

00:12:38.510 --> 00:12:39.910
I came especially to thank you.

00:12:43.000 --> 00:12:44.320
Strictly speaking,

00:12:44.550 --> 00:12:46.200
you're the matchmaker
for Lin Chen and me.

00:12:46.870 --> 00:12:48.150
Lin Chen and I talked it over.

00:12:48.960 --> 00:12:51.480
We're more than happy to have you

00:12:51.870 --> 00:12:53.270
witness our wedding.

00:12:54.440 --> 00:12:55.280
The invitation.

00:12:56.910 --> 00:12:58.510
I'll send it to your home.

00:13:03.320 --> 00:13:04.240
Well, congratulations.

00:13:10.120 --> 00:13:11.150
How do you think

00:13:11.720 --> 00:13:14.240
Bei would feel if his girlfriend were

00:13:14.750 --> 00:13:15.750
marrying someone else?

00:13:18.120 --> 00:13:19.550
He never goes to the bar.

00:13:20.550 --> 00:13:21.750
But he did that day.

00:13:23.030 --> 00:13:24.550
Even offered to drive you.

00:13:25.550 --> 00:13:26.670
To you,

00:13:27.480 --> 00:13:29.600
this might be the start of
your romantic love story.

00:13:30.960 --> 00:13:32.150
But to him,

00:13:33.000 --> 00:13:33.840
maybe,

00:13:33.900 --> 00:13:35.600
it was just drowning his sorrows
in alcohol.

00:13:41.960 --> 00:13:43.670
That's only your guess.

00:13:46.840 --> 00:13:48.150
You can comfort yourself with that.

00:13:49.550 --> 00:13:51.630
Or you could really think it through.

00:13:52.790 --> 00:13:54.360
Why can he accept your past

00:13:54.360 --> 00:13:55.550
so casually?

00:13:56.320 --> 00:13:58.480
And even your ambiguity
with his best friend?

00:13:59.870 --> 00:14:01.390
Is it possible that

00:14:02.000 --> 00:14:03.360
he doesn't care at all.

00:14:09.840 --> 00:14:11.320
Why are you telling me all this?

00:14:16.550 --> 00:14:17.870
Because I really like him.

00:14:18.630 --> 00:14:19.470
And?

00:14:19.670 --> 00:14:21.120
So I think you don't deserve him.

00:14:22.030 --> 00:14:23.670
You're tangled up with so many men.

00:14:24.670 --> 00:14:26.550
Yet you still put on a pure act for him.

00:14:27.670 --> 00:14:28.510
I know.

00:14:28.840 --> 00:14:30.200
Bei doesn't love me.

00:14:31.500 --> 00:14:32.440
But I've been wondering.

00:14:32.670 --> 00:14:34.150
Maybe he doesn't love you either.

00:14:35.870 --> 00:14:37.790
You're just a replacement
for another woman.

00:14:39.200 --> 00:14:40.960
Hi, have you played before?

00:14:41.480 --> 00:14:42.320
I have.

00:14:43.440 --> 00:14:44.280
Mr. Li.

00:14:45.000 --> 00:14:46.120
Could you give me some tips?

00:14:47.600 --> 00:14:49.510
Treat the bullseye as
something you hate the most.

00:14:49.510 --> 00:14:51.200
Or something you want to
get rid of the most.

00:14:52.000 --> 00:14:53.270
This way, you won't hesitate.

00:14:59.150 --> 00:14:59.990
Of course.

00:15:01.000 --> 00:15:03.600
If you choose to keep lying to yourself,

00:15:04.550 --> 00:15:05.720
that's your choice.

00:15:19.270 --> 00:15:20.270
Do you still remember?

00:15:20.750 --> 00:15:21.600
Back then,

00:15:22.100 --> 00:15:23.390
you taught me how to exert force.

00:15:23.910 --> 00:15:25.150
How to hit the bullseye.

00:15:26.150 --> 00:15:28.120
But I just couldn't hit it
no matter what I did.

00:15:32.120 --> 00:15:33.320
Haven't played in ages, right?

00:15:33.630 --> 00:15:34.470
Try again.

00:15:49.620 --> 00:15:51.080
Let's go back to the way things were.

00:15:52.360 --> 00:15:53.200
Okay?

00:16:02.510 --> 00:16:03.350
Zhen.

00:16:05.790 --> 00:16:06.790
We can't go back.

00:16:08.750 --> 00:16:09.590
Why not?

00:16:11.240 --> 00:16:12.270
I have a girlfriend now.

00:16:17.840 --> 00:16:18.680
I'm sorry.

00:16:22.270 --> 00:16:23.510
Maybe this apology

00:16:24.550 --> 00:16:25.600
comes a little too late.

00:16:28.790 --> 00:16:30.000
But I still hope

00:16:31.360 --> 00:16:32.630
we don't part with resentment.

00:16:34.240 --> 00:16:35.390
I still think of you a lot.

00:16:36.360 --> 00:16:37.240
Think of

00:16:37.440 --> 00:16:38.550
how cute you are,

00:16:39.360 --> 00:16:40.320
how much energy you have,

00:16:40.720 --> 00:16:42.360
how you go after what you want.

00:16:44.630 --> 00:16:45.470
Of course,

00:16:47.380 --> 00:16:49.120
I also remember
all the good you did for me.

00:16:51.670 --> 00:16:52.870
If our breakup

00:16:53.500 --> 00:16:54.630
could've been a little gentler,

00:16:56.650 --> 00:16:58.200
those memories would all be beautiful.

00:17:04.110 --> 00:17:05.510
Now that girl...

00:17:07.720 --> 00:17:08.560
Do you love her?

00:17:10.160 --> 00:17:11.030
Her name is Li Xiaoxi.

00:17:12.720 --> 00:17:13.560
I love her.

00:17:17.270 --> 00:17:18.350
You want to go find her?

00:17:22.400 --> 00:17:23.240
Yes.

00:17:25.000 --> 00:17:25.840
Alright.

00:17:26.100 --> 00:17:27.080
Then you have my blessing.

00:17:29.200 --> 00:17:30.720
Treat her well from now on.

00:17:31.790 --> 00:17:33.440
Don't make the same mistake again.

00:17:38.220 --> 00:17:41.230
♪I♪

00:17:42.440 --> 00:17:43.350
You take care too.

00:17:51.720 --> 00:17:55.330
♪I♪

00:17:56.110 --> 00:17:57.200
Xiaoxi, where are you?

00:18:00.750 --> 00:18:01.590
Alright.

00:18:01.750 --> 00:18:02.590
I'll come find you.

00:18:04.430 --> 00:18:09.230
♪So I'm waiting♪

00:18:10.680 --> 00:18:14.810
♪Waiting for the right♪

00:18:18.790 --> 00:18:20.000
Here, coffee.

00:18:37.550 --> 00:18:38.480
It's all over now.

00:18:40.720 --> 00:18:42.160
Did you say everything you wanted to?

00:18:43.480 --> 00:18:44.320
Mm.

00:18:45.510 --> 00:18:46.590
I never thought,

00:18:47.510 --> 00:18:48.830
after waiting for so many years,

00:18:50.030 --> 00:18:51.640
all I'd get is a farewell.

00:18:53.310 --> 00:18:55.030
Do you think I'm ridiculous?

00:18:57.200 --> 00:18:58.040
Not at all.

00:18:59.720 --> 00:19:02.070
Someone who holds onto their first love
for so long.

00:19:02.480 --> 00:19:03.680
Why would it be ridiculous?

00:19:05.030 --> 00:19:06.000
Just

00:19:09.440 --> 00:19:11.110
heartbreakingly naive.

00:19:17.270 --> 00:19:18.350
But this is a good thing.

00:19:19.960 --> 00:19:21.510
Now you can start thinking about me.

00:19:27.640 --> 00:19:29.790
Today drained you emotionally.

00:19:30.350 --> 00:19:32.160
We should treat ourselves to
a good meal.

00:19:33.960 --> 00:19:34.800
Shall we go?

00:19:36.350 --> 00:19:37.190
Mm.

00:19:53.400 --> 00:19:54.240
Xiaoxi.

00:19:55.030 --> 00:19:55.870
I'm sorry.

00:19:57.160 --> 00:19:58.440
I was wrong before.

00:19:59.070 --> 00:20:00.310
I shouldn't have avoided you.

00:20:01.060 --> 00:20:02.160
Shouldn't have hidden from you.

00:20:06.030 --> 00:20:07.350
Can I ask you a few questions?

00:20:12.070 --> 00:20:13.440
Your store is called Zhen Guan.

00:20:14.720 --> 00:20:16.350
Is it because
you still can't forget her?

00:20:17.160 --> 00:20:18.000
No.

00:20:19.240 --> 00:20:20.920
At first, it was out of spite.

00:20:21.720 --> 00:20:22.920
I wanted her to see

00:20:23.440 --> 00:20:24.280
that I made it.

00:20:25.270 --> 00:20:26.310
And your car.

00:20:27.120 --> 00:20:28.160
It breaks down all the time.

00:20:28.160 --> 00:20:29.640
But you never want to replace it.

00:20:30.960 --> 00:20:31.830
Is that also because

00:20:31.830 --> 00:20:33.350
you bought it when you were with her?

00:20:34.000 --> 00:20:35.270
Why not drive mine instead?

00:20:35.270 --> 00:20:36.550
I hardly drive anyway.

00:20:36.830 --> 00:20:37.670
No need.

00:20:38.270 --> 00:20:39.590
I'm used to this one.

00:20:39.830 --> 00:20:40.750
I've driven it for years.

00:20:42.030 --> 00:20:43.200
And that sakura chocolate.

00:20:44.590 --> 00:20:46.270
You always stock up on a ton of it.

00:20:46.550 --> 00:20:47.880
Is that also because she loved it?

00:20:49.270 --> 00:20:50.160
Xiaoxi.

00:20:50.160 --> 00:20:51.640
I bought the sakura chocolate

00:20:51.640 --> 00:20:52.480
you like.

00:20:54.510 --> 00:20:55.400
And Lin Chen.

00:20:56.920 --> 00:20:57.790
You hate him so much.

00:20:58.240 --> 00:20:59.350
You beat him up like that.

00:20:59.960 --> 00:21:01.590
It wasn't because
you were jealous of me.

00:21:02.160 --> 00:21:03.960
It was because he took your Zhen away.

00:21:04.790 --> 00:21:06.000
It's not what you think.

00:21:06.000 --> 00:21:07.030
Also, I'm curious

00:21:07.500 --> 00:21:09.350
if you two still stay in touch
after the breakup?

00:21:09.930 --> 00:21:11.310
I haven't had any contact with her.

00:21:11.540 --> 00:21:12.960
The only time she ever came to see me

00:21:12.970 --> 00:21:13.830
was to tell me

00:21:13.830 --> 00:21:15.350
that she was marrying Lin Chen.

00:21:15.920 --> 00:21:16.760
When was that?

00:21:22.270 --> 00:21:23.110
Six months ago.

00:21:24.750 --> 00:21:25.590
What day?

00:21:31.070 --> 00:21:32.070
The day I met you.

00:21:32.720 --> 00:21:33.640
Were you alone?

00:21:40.070 --> 00:21:40.910
Yeah.

00:21:54.270 --> 00:21:55.400
Thanks for being honest.

00:22:00.110 --> 00:22:01.310
That day, I guess,

00:22:02.590 --> 00:22:04.270
anyone who showed up at the bar,

00:22:05.060 --> 00:22:06.240
anyone who was there by your side,

00:22:06.240 --> 00:22:07.200
could've filled that void.

00:22:07.200 --> 00:22:08.160
It didn't have to be me.

00:22:09.550 --> 00:22:11.880
I was just a replacement from the start.

00:22:12.720 --> 00:22:14.790
I need to talk to you about my past.

00:22:15.550 --> 00:22:17.110
If I'm guessing right,

00:22:17.170 --> 00:22:18.480
it's about another man, isn't it?

00:22:18.750 --> 00:22:20.270
You have the right to know my past.

00:22:20.720 --> 00:22:22.030
I know what to ask and

00:22:22.030 --> 00:22:23.200
what not to.

00:22:23.780 --> 00:22:25.110
Besides, you don't want to talk.

00:22:25.510 --> 00:22:26.720
Why torture yourself here?

00:22:26.930 --> 00:22:28.270
You pretend to be tolerant of me.

00:22:28.960 --> 00:22:30.270
Never asking me for anything.

00:22:30.440 --> 00:22:31.640
Now I finally understand that

00:22:35.590 --> 00:22:36.830
it wasn't acceptance.

00:22:39.160 --> 00:22:41.000
And it wasn't generosity either.

00:22:42.640 --> 00:22:43.880
It's that you don't...

00:22:44.790 --> 00:22:46.920
You don't love...

00:22:48.480 --> 00:22:51.110
You never truly loved me.

00:22:51.110 --> 00:22:52.590
So you don't care!

00:22:52.920 --> 00:22:54.200
It's not what you think.

00:22:56.110 --> 00:22:57.790
I put up with you because I love you.

00:22:58.010 --> 00:22:59.070
I don't care about all that,

00:22:59.070 --> 00:23:00.550
because I'm just scared of losing you.

00:23:01.440 --> 00:23:03.070
Whether it's Lin Chen or Zhen now,

00:23:03.070 --> 00:23:04.510
they have nothing to do with me anymore.

00:23:07.070 --> 00:23:07.910
Xiaoxi.

00:23:10.480 --> 00:23:11.400
You're the one I...

00:23:12.310 --> 00:23:14.480
The one I want to share my life with.

00:23:14.880 --> 00:23:16.070
Sharing the life.

00:23:17.200 --> 00:23:18.110
That's the key.

00:23:18.510 --> 00:23:19.440
Sharing the life.

00:23:20.810 --> 00:23:22.830
Find someone you don't love
but who's suitable for marriage.

00:23:22.860 --> 00:23:24.200
Then you'll never get hurt again.

00:23:24.350 --> 00:23:25.190
No.

00:23:25.500 --> 00:23:26.510
Just need someone to be with.

00:23:27.000 --> 00:23:28.400
Then we'll have a kid.

00:23:28.730 --> 00:23:29.750
Pretend to love each other.

00:23:29.750 --> 00:23:31.070
Live a lifetime of lies.

00:23:31.200 --> 00:23:32.590
Is that what you want?

00:23:34.750 --> 00:23:35.590
I...

00:23:37.160 --> 00:23:38.720
I love you.

00:23:38.720 --> 00:23:40.440
If this is what you call love,

00:23:49.350 --> 00:23:50.350
then take it back.

00:24:34.750 --> 00:24:36.510
I thought this wild rose suits you.

00:24:38.550 --> 00:24:39.440
So I just bought one.

00:24:43.590 --> 00:24:44.680
I don't wanna hear anything.

00:24:45.050 --> 00:24:46.070
I have something to say to you.

00:24:46.300 --> 00:24:47.550
I know what you're going to say.

00:24:48.360 --> 00:24:49.590
I haven't even said it, how do you...

00:24:54.830 --> 00:24:55.960
Why are you crying?

00:25:01.070 --> 00:25:02.350
I don't want to make you cry.

00:25:11.200 --> 00:25:12.040
They always say

00:25:14.550 --> 00:25:16.590
the best liars even fool themselves.

00:25:19.310 --> 00:25:21.030
I'm that liar who fooled myself.

00:25:22.880 --> 00:25:24.510
But I'm the dumbest one of all.

00:25:28.110 --> 00:25:29.310
I can't fool Bei.

00:25:29.830 --> 00:25:30.750
And I can't fool you.

00:25:32.590 --> 00:25:33.790
I only fooled myself.

00:25:36.680 --> 00:25:38.070
I came up with a theory

00:25:38.310 --> 00:25:39.880
that I never really wanted to have you.

00:25:40.480 --> 00:25:42.680
But that's all crap. It's all a lie.

00:25:46.220 --> 00:25:48.110
Do you still remember
that little boy's puzzle?

00:25:51.330 --> 00:25:52.830
I was scared that
the person I liked the most

00:25:52.830 --> 00:25:54.310
would become someone I hated.

00:25:56.400 --> 00:25:57.680
So I ran away.

00:25:58.350 --> 00:25:59.640
Did nothing at all.

00:26:02.440 --> 00:26:03.680
But I can't wait. Not one more minute.

00:26:03.680 --> 00:26:05.400
Not one more second.

00:26:06.110 --> 00:26:08.000
I'm not afraid of
being thrown out at the start.

00:26:08.880 --> 00:26:10.960
I'm afraid
I won't even have the courage to play.

00:26:20.830 --> 00:26:22.550
I don't love that perfect woman,

00:26:22.750 --> 00:26:23.590
Jiang Yifan.

00:26:27.510 --> 00:26:28.480
The one I love is you,

00:26:38.400 --> 00:26:39.240
Xiaoxi.

00:26:42.880 --> 00:26:43.990
It's you I love.

00:26:43.990 --> 00:26:46.930
♪If it can't be stopped,
I say let it be♪

00:26:49.720 --> 00:26:53.070
♪This is a battle of desire and despair♪

00:26:56.570 --> 00:27:00.060
♪The lingering warmth,
she likes to leave♪

00:27:02.020 --> 00:27:03.600
♪On her way out♪

00:27:04.060 --> 00:27:06.440
♪She casually turned off the light♪

00:27:11.030 --> 00:27:12.110
Did you ever

00:27:15.200 --> 00:27:17.350
have even a little crush on me?

00:27:25.510 --> 00:27:26.920
Even for a moment.

00:27:38.590 --> 00:27:40.000
Did you ever,

00:27:42.030 --> 00:27:43.640
even just a little,

00:27:44.200 --> 00:27:45.110
just a tiny bit,

00:27:46.440 --> 00:27:47.750
have feelings for me?

00:27:49.840 --> 00:27:53.220
♪If it can't be stopped,
I say let it be♪

00:27:56.610 --> 00:27:59.770
♪Hanging onto the innocence
that should be mine♪

00:28:03.180 --> 00:28:06.340
♪Ups and downs with joys and sorrows♪

00:28:08.680 --> 00:28:10.550
♪Let go of the rope♪

00:28:10.810 --> 00:28:12.950
♪At worst, no one will care♪

00:28:50.960 --> 00:28:52.590
What's going on here?

00:28:53.070 --> 00:28:54.000
Are you moving?

00:28:54.920 --> 00:28:55.760
We're closing down.

00:28:56.790 --> 00:28:59.030
What do you mean by closing down?

00:28:59.960 --> 00:29:00.960
I'm out of business.

00:29:02.550 --> 00:29:04.880
This collection is really popular.

00:29:05.160 --> 00:29:06.590
So I licensed the brand out.

00:29:07.160 --> 00:29:08.640
Why do you always act on impulse?

00:29:08.820 --> 00:29:10.680
Why didn't you
discuss this big decision with me?

00:29:12.310 --> 00:29:13.880
It's time to hit pause for a while.

00:29:14.240 --> 00:29:16.880
You just made some money
and built a reputation.

00:29:16.880 --> 00:29:19.680
And now you're messing things up again.
What do you want?

00:29:21.400 --> 00:29:22.240
Going abroad for study.

00:29:25.310 --> 00:29:26.150
How old are you?

00:29:27.880 --> 00:29:30.030
Do you know what really matters in life?

00:29:31.110 --> 00:29:32.830
While Hua still cares about you,

00:29:32.830 --> 00:29:34.400
shouldn't you grab that chance?

00:29:34.400 --> 00:29:35.550
Instead, you're running off abroad.

00:29:36.000 --> 00:29:37.400
Do you know how many girls

00:29:37.590 --> 00:29:38.590
are chasing after him?

00:29:38.790 --> 00:29:40.790
Now you've lost your chance.

00:29:40.790 --> 00:29:42.270
Get it straight.

00:29:42.270 --> 00:29:43.110
Mom.

00:29:43.640 --> 00:29:44.680
In your eyes,

00:29:45.160 --> 00:29:47.440
is Hua my last chance in life?

00:29:54.440 --> 00:29:56.160
If you'd listened to me back then,

00:29:57.350 --> 00:29:59.200
you wouldn't have messed up

00:29:59.480 --> 00:30:00.790
your marriage so badly.

00:30:02.880 --> 00:30:03.920
When you're old,

00:30:04.500 --> 00:30:05.480
and you finally understand.

00:30:06.510 --> 00:30:08.110
It'll be too late to regret it.

00:30:12.480 --> 00:30:13.790
I made my own choices.

00:30:14.030 --> 00:30:15.070
And I won't regret them.

00:30:16.830 --> 00:30:17.670
Back then,

00:30:18.580 --> 00:30:20.110
I was always scared I'd embarrass you.

00:30:20.800 --> 00:30:21.960
Scared of embarrassing myself.

00:30:21.960 --> 00:30:23.790
(Yu: I'm no good with gifts or words.
I just want you happy.)

00:30:23.790 --> 00:30:25.200
It sounds ridiculous now.

00:30:25.720 --> 00:30:26.750
So exhausting.

00:30:29.000 --> 00:30:30.300
(Hide from; Tag: Private; Friends: Xiu)

00:30:30.310 --> 00:30:31.550
Actually, in life,

00:30:32.200 --> 00:30:34.070
(Handmade by my husband)
your own happiness comes first.

00:30:34.790 --> 00:30:36.200
What others think or say

00:30:36.200 --> 00:30:37.310
doesn't really matter.

00:30:41.270 --> 00:30:42.440
Could you close the door

00:30:42.590 --> 00:30:43.880
on your way out?

00:30:52.000 --> 00:30:52.840
Here, here.

00:31:01.640 --> 00:31:02.960
This is your new home.

00:31:03.240 --> 00:31:04.080
Do you like it?

00:31:11.900 --> 00:31:16.580
(Music isn't entertainment.
It's the natural rhythm of life.)

00:31:30.600 --> 00:31:34.570
♪In the story of love, there are many♪

00:31:34.570 --> 00:31:37.400
♪Different twists and turns♪

00:31:38.560 --> 00:31:42.060
♪You're my little joy♪

00:31:42.060 --> 00:31:45.930
♪So precious and beautiful in my heart♪

00:31:46.590 --> 00:31:49.830
♪Is all about us you and me♪

00:31:49.830 --> 00:31:54.090
♪I love getting lost in this feeling♪

00:31:54.580 --> 00:31:58.230
♪You and me, in your eyes♪

00:31:58.350 --> 00:32:01.650
♪I search for my reflection♪

00:32:05.380 --> 00:32:09.660
♪These belong to♪

00:32:13.350 --> 00:32:15.590
♪It's all about♪

00:32:15.590 --> 00:32:17.870
♪You and me♪

00:32:22.330 --> 00:32:25.830
♪All about us♪

00:32:26.550 --> 00:32:32.420
♪You're my cherished unicorn♪

00:32:34.560 --> 00:32:39.830
♪You're my cherished unicorn♪

00:33:15.880 --> 00:33:16.720
Sen.

00:33:17.000 --> 00:33:17.960
What are you doing here?

00:33:18.920 --> 00:33:20.000
If you miss me,

00:33:21.000 --> 00:33:22.310
across the Qin River to me.

00:33:23.160 --> 00:33:24.160
If you don't,

00:33:24.900 --> 00:33:26.070
there are plenty of others who will.

00:33:26.790 --> 00:33:28.310
You silly fool.

00:33:29.240 --> 00:33:30.440
Wherever you go, I'll go too.

00:33:31.200 --> 00:33:32.920
I told you already.

00:33:34.880 --> 00:33:35.960
This time, it's different.

00:33:37.680 --> 00:33:38.520
The ring!

00:33:54.830 --> 00:33:55.670
Mingming.

00:33:58.400 --> 00:33:59.240
I love you.

00:34:14.220 --> 00:34:15.230
They kissed They kissed!

00:34:15.230 --> 00:34:16.070
They kissed!

00:34:16.920 --> 00:34:18.440
What's up front? Are we moving or not?

00:34:18.710 --> 00:34:20.070
Hold on, someone's proposing!

00:34:20.960 --> 00:34:22.320
A proposing. Give it a second.

00:34:29.510 --> 00:34:30.480
Sirs,

00:34:31.360 --> 00:34:32.200
I'm sorry.

00:34:34.440 --> 00:34:35.710
Because of my own unreliability,

00:34:37.320 --> 00:34:38.480
I caused you some trouble.

00:34:46.800 --> 00:34:48.030
If the fan concert is still on,

00:34:49.000 --> 00:34:50.280
I'll go back and rehearse right away.

00:34:50.400 --> 00:34:51.920
I've already
finished the music arrangement.

00:34:52.190 --> 00:34:54.000
Every song will sound
even better than before.

00:34:55.300 --> 00:34:56.590
I hope you can give me another chance.

00:35:03.900 --> 00:35:07.460
(Liang)

00:35:07.480 --> 00:35:09.360
Why is the flower shop closed?

00:35:12.320 --> 00:35:13.280
Where's Xiaoxi?

00:35:15.260 --> 00:35:16.460
(Shop for transfer)

00:35:20.510 --> 00:35:21.350
Yingtao.

00:35:22.030 --> 00:35:22.920
Have you seen Xiaoxi?

00:35:23.710 --> 00:35:25.710
No, wasn't she with you?

00:35:27.360 --> 00:35:28.200
If she contacts you,

00:35:28.360 --> 00:35:29.200
please let me know.

00:35:30.960 --> 00:35:32.070
What did you do to her?

00:35:40.180 --> 00:35:41.380
(Xiaoxi)

00:35:42.840 --> 00:35:43.680
Sorry,

00:35:43.960 --> 00:35:46.880
the number you dialed
is currently unavailable.

00:35:48.020 --> 00:35:50.380
(Xiaoxi's Father)

00:35:56.440 --> 00:35:57.880
Hello, who's this?

00:35:57.880 --> 00:35:58.760
Uncle,

00:35:58.760 --> 00:36:00.110
it's me, Bei.

00:36:00.110 --> 00:36:01.030
I was wondering,

00:36:01.550 --> 00:36:02.800
do you know where Xiaoxi is?

00:36:03.280 --> 00:36:04.120
I have no idea.

00:36:04.840 --> 00:36:06.400
Is something wrong with Xi?

00:36:07.030 --> 00:36:08.550
I went to find her just now.

00:36:08.550 --> 00:36:09.880
But her flower shop's been sold.

00:36:09.930 --> 00:36:10.920
She's nowhere to be found.

00:36:10.920 --> 00:36:11.760
No one's home either.

00:36:12.020 --> 00:36:13.320
Do you have any clue where she might go?

00:36:14.070 --> 00:36:15.280
How would I know?

00:36:15.440 --> 00:36:17.150
I'm busy right now. I'm hanging up.

00:36:17.150 --> 00:36:17.990
Hello?

00:36:30.960 --> 00:36:32.590
Why is it so quiet in here?

00:36:33.440 --> 00:36:34.920
When she came home last night,

00:36:34.920 --> 00:36:36.630
she went straight into her room.

00:36:38.070 --> 00:36:39.440
Didn't say a single word.

00:36:42.150 --> 00:36:43.400
Did she tell you anything?

00:36:44.510 --> 00:36:45.350
Nothing.

00:36:45.630 --> 00:36:46.630
This kid, seriously,

00:36:46.840 --> 00:36:47.710
wouldn't even eat.

00:36:47.710 --> 00:36:49.230
How can her body take this?

00:37:06.280 --> 00:37:07.760
How is it? Did you reach her?

00:37:08.000 --> 00:37:08.840
No.

00:37:10.920 --> 00:37:11.760
Bei Qiyuan.

00:37:12.360 --> 00:37:13.480
Bei Qiyuan, get out here now!

00:37:13.800 --> 00:37:15.000
Bei Qiyuan, you blockhead!

00:37:15.670 --> 00:37:16.920
Gong, Gong, talk it out nicely.

00:37:16.920 --> 00:37:17.920
- Don't stop me!
- Stay calm.

00:37:17.920 --> 00:37:18.840
I'm gonna fight him!

00:37:19.400 --> 00:37:20.280
Don't stop me!

00:37:20.430 --> 00:37:21.320
Sen, come on.

00:37:21.320 --> 00:37:22.510
Let him go, let him go.

00:37:25.340 --> 00:37:26.360
What are you trying to do?

00:37:26.360 --> 00:37:27.200
Stay away from me!

00:37:29.380 --> 00:37:30.230
Where's Xiaoxi?

00:37:30.230 --> 00:37:31.510
Why do you care where my wife is?

00:37:31.510 --> 00:37:32.920
Pooh, you don't deserve her.

00:37:33.130 --> 00:37:34.480
Not married yet, so it doesn't count.

00:37:34.840 --> 00:37:35.710
You're her almost-ex.

00:37:35.710 --> 00:37:37.110
Don't say those two words
in front of me.

00:37:37.360 --> 00:37:39.400
Our argument has nothing to do with you.

00:37:41.760 --> 00:37:43.510
I've told you so many times.

00:37:43.510 --> 00:37:44.840
Treat Xiaoxi well.

00:37:47.150 --> 00:37:48.400
Since you won't listen,

00:37:48.400 --> 00:37:49.590
then I'll just come clean.

00:37:50.440 --> 00:37:52.230
I like Xiaoxi. I'm gonna pursue her.

00:37:52.840 --> 00:37:54.480
From now on, you have a serious rival!

00:37:55.070 --> 00:37:56.030
I already talked to her.

00:37:56.030 --> 00:37:57.190
She'll let me know in a few days.

00:37:57.190 --> 00:37:58.400
I'll call her right now.

00:38:01.700 --> 00:38:02.540
(Voice Call)

00:38:02.900 --> 00:38:04.140
(Not friends, No calls)

00:38:09.170 --> 00:38:10.030
Hello?

00:38:10.030 --> 00:38:10.880
Xiaoxi.

00:38:11.280 --> 00:38:12.120
Mm.

00:38:12.360 --> 00:38:13.920
Oh, what? You miss me?

00:38:14.150 --> 00:38:15.840
I miss you too. I'll wait for you to…

00:38:17.040 --> 00:38:18.400
(Not friends, No calls)
Blocked.

00:38:21.550 --> 00:38:22.550
I never thought

00:38:23.440 --> 00:38:24.440
you got blocked too.

00:38:29.000 --> 00:38:31.110
It's him who upset you, not me.

00:38:31.110 --> 00:38:33.320
Why are you taking it out on me, Xiaoxi?

00:38:38.300 --> 00:38:40.820
(Xiaoxi)

00:38:41.320 --> 00:38:42.510
This must be a misunderstanding.

00:38:42.920 --> 00:38:44.360
I'll send a friend request again.

00:38:45.190 --> 00:38:46.880
She blocked you,
so even if you apply again,

00:38:47.070 --> 00:38:47.920
she won't even see it.

00:38:47.920 --> 00:38:49.190
Enough with the nonsense.

00:39:58.550 --> 00:39:59.670
Professor Cheng.

00:40:00.070 --> 00:40:00.910
Hello.

00:40:02.100 --> 00:40:02.960
Long time no see.

00:40:02.960 --> 00:40:04.230
Yeah, it's been a while.

00:40:04.800 --> 00:40:05.710
What brings you here?

00:40:05.920 --> 00:40:07.110
This is my hometown.

00:40:08.070 --> 00:40:09.360
And you? What are you doing here?

00:40:09.800 --> 00:40:12.400
Our lab happened to
come to your village for

00:40:12.550 --> 00:40:13.630
flower variety improvement.

00:40:13.780 --> 00:40:15.070
Two of my graduate students wanted to

00:40:15.090 --> 00:40:16.960
do an internship here,
so I brought them along.

00:40:18.190 --> 00:40:19.030
What a coincidence.

00:40:19.280 --> 00:40:20.120
Yes.

00:40:22.710 --> 00:40:23.550
Sorry.

00:40:24.230 --> 00:40:26.190
For approaching you that way back then.

00:40:30.110 --> 00:40:31.360
Actually, to be honest,

00:40:31.590 --> 00:40:32.960
I should be the one apologizing.

00:40:35.230 --> 00:40:36.440
I took advantage of you.

00:40:37.840 --> 00:40:39.150
Even though I might seem

00:40:39.480 --> 00:40:41.880
like a total bookworm,

00:40:42.320 --> 00:40:43.440
I wasn't that clueless.

00:40:44.190 --> 00:40:46.320
I never thought someone like you,

00:40:46.710 --> 00:40:49.480
who chases
independent spirit and free thinking,

00:40:50.550 --> 00:40:53.110
would be trapped by love
for 20 whole years.

00:40:56.880 --> 00:40:57.880
Sorry, Professor Cheng.

00:40:58.110 --> 00:40:59.030
I have to take this call.

00:41:06.070 --> 00:41:08.280
I never told you that detail about

00:41:08.590 --> 00:41:09.510
our twenty years together.

00:41:09.920 --> 00:41:11.030
How did you even know?

00:41:11.930 --> 00:41:13.440
(Points to the recording)
So I suspected

00:41:13.800 --> 00:41:15.000
you knew her well.

00:41:16.510 --> 00:41:17.350
Sorry.

00:41:19.230 --> 00:41:20.320
It's fine. It's okay.

00:41:20.320 --> 00:41:21.160
Here.

00:41:23.110 --> 00:41:24.480
Here, clean this up.

00:41:24.880 --> 00:41:25.760
Come, take a look.

00:41:29.400 --> 00:41:30.670
You're like a detective Conan.

00:41:32.110 --> 00:41:33.800
Maybe I was just
too desperate to leave her.

00:41:33.960 --> 00:41:34.800
A little too sensitive.

00:41:35.760 --> 00:41:36.600
I'm sorry.

00:41:36.880 --> 00:41:38.320
I even broke your phone.

00:41:38.760 --> 00:41:39.600
It's okay.

00:41:41.550 --> 00:41:43.320
You think I'd tell someone. I know.

00:41:46.110 --> 00:41:48.110
I wanted her to give up completely.

00:41:48.590 --> 00:41:49.760
Actually, I knew that day,

00:41:49.960 --> 00:41:51.400
she'd bring her friends over

00:41:51.800 --> 00:41:53.480
to talk business at that time.

00:41:54.190 --> 00:41:55.550
So I just went with it.

00:41:55.760 --> 00:41:57.000
Put on that show.

00:41:57.400 --> 00:41:59.280
So it was me and Guan who got tricked.

00:42:00.030 --> 00:42:01.320
I really tried

00:42:02.360 --> 00:42:04.360
to fix our relationship.

00:42:05.590 --> 00:42:06.800
But she started to

00:42:07.180 --> 00:42:08.440
become more and more controlling.

00:42:08.670 --> 00:42:09.840
The more successful she became.

00:42:10.110 --> 00:42:11.320
The more greedy she got.

00:42:11.840 --> 00:42:13.550
Every day she just thought about

00:42:13.550 --> 00:42:14.880
making more and more money.

00:42:16.840 --> 00:42:18.440
Maybe our values

00:42:19.150 --> 00:42:20.360
grew further and further apart.

00:42:21.280 --> 00:42:22.800
I still prefer

00:42:23.150 --> 00:42:24.590
those raw travels.

00:42:25.840 --> 00:42:27.150
I hate calculating everything every day.

00:42:29.030 --> 00:42:30.320
Honestly, that kind of scene

00:42:30.320 --> 00:42:32.880
would be too cruel,
for any woman to face.

00:42:35.030 --> 00:42:36.630
For being a part of it,

00:42:36.880 --> 00:42:38.000
I even felt ashamed.

00:42:39.230 --> 00:42:40.880
But Guan really loves you.

00:42:42.150 --> 00:42:43.550
To deny all the years

00:42:43.550 --> 00:42:44.440
you spent together.

00:42:44.440 --> 00:42:45.800
It would break her heart.

00:42:49.510 --> 00:42:51.630
I was just so desperate to,
leave her back then.

00:42:52.510 --> 00:42:53.800
I went a little too far.

00:42:56.000 --> 00:42:57.930
You seem to be doing well now.

00:42:57.940 --> 00:42:58.800
Mm.

00:42:58.810 --> 00:43:00.280
I keep myself busy every day.

00:43:02.070 --> 00:43:04.360
Guan really should've

00:43:04.760 --> 00:43:05.600
heard this.

00:43:09.320 --> 00:43:10.760
It doesn't matter. It's all in the past.

00:43:12.000 --> 00:43:13.800
I just hope she's doing well too.

00:43:18.440 --> 00:43:19.960
Well, I'll get back to work.

00:43:21.030 --> 00:43:22.030
Where are you heading?

00:43:22.820 --> 00:43:24.320
There's another flower field up ahead.

00:43:24.320 --> 00:43:25.320
I need to check it out.

00:43:25.920 --> 00:43:27.030
Can I come with you?

00:43:29.320 --> 00:43:30.160
Sure.

00:43:37.060 --> 00:43:39.260
(Li Xiaoxi)

00:43:47.280 --> 00:43:48.760
Are you filming a video?

00:43:49.000 --> 00:43:50.320
Can I send it to Guan?

00:44:16.400 --> 00:44:18.999
♪I'll admit♪

00:44:19.000 --> 00:44:23.039
♪My back is faced against the wall♪

00:44:23.920 --> 00:44:27.786
♪There's nothing that
I wouldn't try to do♪

00:44:27.811 --> 00:44:31.999
♪For this feeling to have you♪

00:44:32.280 --> 00:44:34.479
♪I'll resist♪

00:44:34.800 --> 00:44:36.814
♪Your gaze, your lips♪

00:44:36.839 --> 00:44:38.999
♪Your touches again♪

00:44:39.880 --> 00:44:43.860
♪There's no one that
I wouldn't try to fool♪

00:44:43.885 --> 00:44:46.919
♪For an image of you♪

00:44:47.920 --> 00:44:50.359
♪Take my hand again♪

00:44:50.360 --> 00:44:52.119
♪Take my mind again♪

00:44:52.200 --> 00:44:55.559
♪Break into my heart again♪

00:44:55.960 --> 00:44:58.137
♪I'm falling out again♪

00:44:58.162 --> 00:44:59.999
♪I'm on my knees again♪

00:45:00.000 --> 00:45:03.839
♪To beg for the truth♪

00:45:05.680 --> 00:45:09.839
♪Tell me the secret of love♪

00:45:09.840 --> 00:45:14.839
♪Is that the secret to love♪

00:45:15.200 --> 00:45:18.159
♪I thought it had came from
below us♪

00:45:18.240 --> 00:45:21.639
♪Did it come from above♪

00:45:21.720 --> 00:45:25.479
♪Tell me the secret of love♪

00:45:25.720 --> 00:45:30.799
♪Is that the secret to love♪

00:45:31.200 --> 00:45:33.639
♪Is it violent or warming, entrancing♪

00:45:33.640 --> 00:45:38.079
♪This secret of love♪